item.title: How Much did Stephen Curry Really Change the Way Basketball is Played Today?
item.description: Welcome to my page. My name is Kaden Ross and I am providing a statistical data analysis for my college course at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I am eager to be able to share my analysis and different viewpoints on how Stephen Curry changed the way basketball is played forever.
